Description: Use standard genomic file format to evaluate pair-wise synteny conservation at the genome-wide scale. 
  It takes a table of orthologs and genome annotation files to automatically infer 
  significantly conserved linkage groups, and order them on an Oxford Grid using a network based greedy algorithm.
